Package: Friedman
Title: Tools for Simple Financial and Data Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Kyana", "Hay", email = "kmhay@usf.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    Friedman is an R package designed to support simple financial and
    data analysis workflows. The package will provide functions for
    cleaning data, summarizing results, and creating basic visualizations
    for students and early-stage analysts.
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.1.2)
